picture in the living room with a brooklyn bridge poster on the wall. look for the table near the picture. the table lamp is on the left side of the table. the sofa chair is on the right side of the table. the clock is on the top left corner of the frame.
picture located near a sink in a bathroom.
picture located in a hallway with two paintings on the wall. the picture is spatially relative to the other objects in the scene.
picture of a bathroom with a sink and mirror. the picture is located in the same region as the bathroom cabinet, sink, mirror, and bed.
bathroom with a toilet and framed pictures on the wall. the picture is located below the toilet.
